description: This file defines the routing logic for a Flutter application, mapping route names to corresponding pages such as event forms, birthday forms, and chat pages. It contains a class AppRouter with a static method onGenerateRoute to handle route generation.

classes.name: AppRouter
classes.description: A class that manages named route generation for the Flutter app.

methods.name: onGenerateRoute
methods.description: A static method that generates routes based on the provided RouteSettings, returning appropriate pages or a default 'unknown route' page.
